    <para id="para-00012">As the examples show, single round-robin tournament play can quickly grow in the number of games required to determine a champion. As such, some tournaments elect to employ variations of single round-robin tournament play as well as other tournament styles such as elimination tournaments.</para>
    <figure id="fig-00003">
    <media alt="Insert Alt Text">
