      2, 1</item>
      <item>Describe how the next number in the Lucas sequence is determined and compare this to how the next number is determined in the Fibonacci sequence.<newline/>
      Add the two previous numbers to obtain the next number in the Lucas sequence. The same pattern for finding the next number is used with the Fibonacci sequence.</item>
